Package com.groupone.p2pgame

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CheckerBoard
    CheckerBoard is the main entry point into the checkers board.
    CheckerBoardSpace
    CheckerBoardSpace holds the graphical elements of a "space" in a checker board.
    CheckerBoardState
    Checker board state holds all of the data about the checker board displayed in CheckerBoard.
    CheckerMove
    CheckerMove stores an arbitrary game move that may or may not be valid.
    CheckerSquare
    CheckerSquare holds the data of one square in a checkers game.
    Client
    The client is used to send messages to the server based on the command given from the server these messages will then be passed to the second player
    GameDriver  
    GamePiece
    A game piece UI element that is represented on-screen as an oval.
    Piece
    Piece holds information about a single piece.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    PieceType
    PieceType stores the type of the piece that is being used.
    Player
    Player holds identifiers for each player.
